&lt;ol>
&lt;li>Installed &lt;a href="https://wiki.python.org/moin/BeginnersGuide/Download">Python 3.9+&lt;/a> (including &lt;a href="https://pip.pypa.io/en/stable/installation/">pip&lt;/a> and
